'''''Star Wars Insider'' 76''' is the seventy-sixth issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands on [[May 18]], [[2004]]. This was the final ''Star Wars Insider'' issue published by [[Paizo Publishing]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"From the Editor's Desk"
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Star News]]: From the World of Lucasfilm" {{C|by [[David Fein]] & ''Insider'' Staff}}
*"[[Star Sightings]]" {{C|by [[Benjamin Harper]]}}
*"[[Best of Hyperspace]]" {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]}}
*"[[HoloNet News (Insider)|HoloNet News]]" {{C|by Pablo Hidalgo}}
**"[[CIS Shadowfeed Dispatch 15:3:21 Edition]]"
**"[[Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 15:3:29]]"
*"[[Set Piece]]" &mdash; Hoth Battlefront {{C|by [[Chris Trevas|Christopher Trevas]]}}
*"[[Bookshelf]]" &mdash; A Book [[Elizabeth Hand|Hunter's Bounty]] {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
*"[[Comics Link]]" &mdash; Stop-Motion Animation {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet|Steve Sansweet]]}}
*"[[Toy Box]]" &mdash; The Art of ''Star Wars'' Packaging & the Galactic Heroes {{C|by starwars.hasbro.com}}
*"[[Action Figure Archive]]" {{C|by [[Victor Wertz|Vic Wertz]] with Dan Curto}}
*"[[Crossword (department)|Crossword]]" &mdash; Keeping Score {{C|by [[Michael Selinker]]}}
*"[[Star Wars Q&A|''Star Wars'' Q&A]]" {{C|by Pablo Hidalgo}}
*"[[The Last Page]]" {{C|by [[Tony Moseley]]}}

===Features===
*"[[Prequel Update]] for Episode III" {{C|by [[Jane Irene Kelly]]}}
*:<small>In late March, producer [[Rick McCallum]] went back to the land down under to get ready for shooting [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|Episode III's]]'' much-anticipated [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] scene.</small>
*"[[Blue Sky Minds: The Artists of Episode III]]" {{C|by [[Jenny Scott]]}}
*:<small>The concept artists behind ''Star Wars Episode III'' reveal their secrets.</small>
*"[[Looks Good on Paper: Mastering the Art of Star Wars Origami in Four Lessons|Looks Good on Paper: Mastering the Art of ''Star Wars'' Origami in Four Lessons]]" {{C|by [[Christopher Alexander]]}}
*:<small>Now you can create your own ''[[Star Wars]]'' models with nothing but a few squares of paper.</small>
*"[[The Old Master: Ralph McQuarrie on Designing Star Wars|The Old Master: Ralph McQuarrie on Designing ''Star Wars'']]" {{C|by [[Ron Magid]]}}
*:<small>[[Ralph McQuarrie]] set the tone for all ''[[Star Wars]]'' art to come when he transformed the ideas of [[George Lucas]] into fabulous images.</small>
*"[[Feng Shmi: New Hope for Collectors]]" {{C|by [[Sandy Clark]]}}
*:<small>It might not gather the chi from the surrounding elements to make your home tranquil and prosperous, but ''[[Star Wars]]'' decorating can be a great way to share your love of the saga with houseguests.</small>
*"[[Changing Seasons]] Part 1: Guardian of the People" {{C|by [[Timothy Zahn]]}}
*:<small>This time it is [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] who goes ahead without backup. Before he can fight the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]], however, he must deal with the natives.</small>

